Chinese athlete Cai Jiayun called and thanked his dad immediately after winning the silver medal in the para cross-country skiing men's long distance standing (classic) at the National Biathlon Center in Zhangjiakou, north China's Hebei Province, on Monday. Canadian veteran Brian McKeever added a gold medal in the para cross-country skiing men's long distance vision impaired (classic) to his list of honors in his final Winter Paralympics at the National Biathlon Center in Zhangjiakou, north China's Hebei Province, on Monday.